  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Fix School Truck for 140 Children in Thailand</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will replace the body of our school truck. The current body is wobbled, the floor is decayed, and the iron structure is rusty. As such, those parts can be unsafe for our students when sitting on the truck to go to school or other places for school activities. Therefore, having a new body of the school truck and enough funding to maintain it in the future is essential for the students&apos; reliable transportation.</narrative>
  </description>
